        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "O(log n)"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "O(n log n)",
      "explanation": "Merge Sort always divides the array into halves and takes linear time to merge, resulting in O(n log n) for all cases.",
      "difficulty": "easy"
    },
